SUMMARY:Healing Prayer Ministry
DESCRIPTION:Using techniques taught by Paramhansa Yogananda\, the Healing P
 rayer ministry prays weekly on Zoom for those in need. Those who serve in 
 this way need to be deeply connected with the path of Kriya yoga as brough
 t by Yogananda.  If you would like to join this ministry\, please contact
  us at prayers@anandaportland.org.
