URL:https://anandaportland.org/events/lahiri-mahasaya-meditation-at-the-co
 mmunity/
SUMMARY:Lahiri Mahasaya Meditation at the community
DESCRIPTION:All are welcome to come to the Ananda Portland Community Chapel
  for a special meditation focusing on Lahiri Mahasaya.  6 AM - 7:30 AM\n\
 nSept 26th marks the anniversary of the Mahasamadhi ("great samadhi" or co
 nscious exit) of the great avatar who brought kriya yoga back into the wor
 ld. Read about this disciple of Babaji and his mission in Autobiography of
  a Yogi.\n\nMeditation will be led by an Ananda minister and will include 
 chanting\, a reading and a closing including healing prayers.\n\n&nbsp\;
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://anandaportland.org/wp-content/uploads/20
 20/02/lahiri___retouched__straight_head-275x400-1.jpg
CATEGORIES:Devotional Event,Meditation
LOCATION:Ananda Portland Community Chapel\, 7020 SW Vermont Court\, Portlan
 d\, Oregon\, 97223\, United States
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=7020 SW Vermont Court\, Por
 tland\, Oregon\, 97223\, United States;X-APPLE-RADIUS=100;X-TITLE=Ananda P
 ortland Community Chapel:geo:0,0
END:VEVENT
