BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:3000858@anandaportland.org
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20231021T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20231021T120000
DTSTAMP:20231016T032015Z
URL:https://anandaportland.org/events/devotional-art/
SUMMARY:Devotional Drawing
DESCRIPTION:Cultivate security and resilience through drawing.\nInvest in y
 our emotional well-being and healing journey as the summer is fading into 
 the fall. This class is not just about art\; it's about finding strength\,
  resilience\, and beauty in your pain and mundane reality.\n\nJoin us and 
 let your creativity lead you to a place of devotion and renewal.\n\nDon't 
 miss this opportunity to rise above pain and find healing through the tran
 sformative power of art. Reserve your spot today and embark on a journey o
 f self-discovery and cultivating divine love.\n\nTaught by Pooja\n\nWhy At
 tend?\n Unlock Your Creative Potential: Tap into your inner artist and h
 arness the therapeutic power of drawing to express your emotions and exper
 iences.\n\n Embrace Healing: Discover how art can be a powerful tool for
  healing emotional wounds\, offering you a safe and supportive space to pr
 ocess your pain.\n\n Guidance: Learn from a presenter who will guide you
  through exercises designed to help you rise above your pain.\n\n Connect
  with Others: Join a community of individuals on their own healing journe
 ys\, sharing insights and encouragement.\n\nClass out line:\n10 AM  praye
 r\, introduction\n10:15 AM - 2 Yoga poses and 15 min meditation.\n10:35 AM
  - Collaborative and individual art practice for an hour. ( paper\, pencil
  and colors will be provided)\n11.35 AM - Sharing\n12 noon - Conclusion\nL
 ight snack and drink will be provided.\n\n\nCost: $15 includes materials\,
  per person\n\n\n
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://anandaportland.org/wp-content/uploads/20
 23/10/Devotional-Drawing-4.jpg
CATEGORIES:Classes
LOCATION:Ananda Temple and Teaching Center\, 4855 SW Watson Ave\, Beaverton
 \, OR\, 97005\, United States
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=4855 SW Watson Ave\, Beaver
 ton\, OR\, 97005\, United States;X-APPLE-RADIUS=100;X-TITLE=Ananda Temple 
 and Teaching Center:geo:0,0
END:VEVENT
