URL:https://anandaportland.org/events/meditation-workshop-with-hanuman/
SUMMARY:Meditation Workshop with Hanuman
DESCRIPTION:Learn the ancient science of meditation taught by Paramhansa Yo
 gananda in this 2 hour workshop. Meditation is a tool for transformation a
 nd spiritual growth that will affect every part of your life\, as you disc
 over calmness and inner peace.\n\nYou will learn:\n\n 	How to sit and keep
  the body still\n 	Where to focus your attention\n 	The Hong Sau technique
  of concentration that is the first step on the path of kriya yoga\n 	How 
 to begin a regular meditation practice and how to keep up your practice\n 
 	Ways to incorporate meditation into your daily (and busy!) life\n 	Resour
 ces you can draw on after this class\n\nIncluded: a meditation manual\n\n\
 n\nTaught by Nayaswami Hanuman\, MTT\, a devotee of Paramhansa Yogananda\,
  with decades of experience to share.
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://anandaportland.org/wp-content/uploads/20
 19/07/group-Meditation-image-cropped.jpg
CATEGORIES:Classes
LOCATION:Ananda Temple and Teaching Center\, 4855 SW Watson Ave\, Beaverton
 \, OR\, 97005\, United States
