SUMMARY:Kirtan at the Temple
DESCRIPTION:Kirtan is a time of shared devotional chanting\, with brief per
 iods of meditation and stillness. Tonight we will have a harp\, harmonium 
 and percussion to lead us into joy. All can participate - no experience ne
 cessary!\n\nChants are by Swami Kriyananda and Paramhansa Yogananda. The w
 ords will be provided and most of the chants are in English. Come open you
 r heart and feel connected to the Divine Presence in all that is.\n\nKirta
 ns are free and your financial support is always welcome.
