 h cleaning and decorating the rest of the space. Lunch will be served.\n\n
 Families are invited to come at 11 am for special kid friendly activities 
 with Teacher Melissa.\n\nTimeline: \n\n10 am - Opening prayer and start t
 he Christmas fun\n\n11 am - 11:45 - Families have special activities toget
 her\n\n12 noon - 1 pm - Lunch will be served for all\n\n1 pm - 2 pm - fini
 shing and clean up\nIt's your temple!  Come make it beautiful for Christm
 as!
