SUMMARY:Book Study: Conversations with Yogananda
DESCRIPTION:Our new book study will be on "Conversations with Yogananda" by
  Swami Kriyananda. These are words straight from the great avatar\, spoken
  and recorded by his direct disciple. The truth and power in these convers
 ations gives endless possibilities for discussion.\n\nWe will be meeting w
 eekly\, over Zoom\, to explore the entire book.\n\nMondays @ 5pm - 6pm\n\n
 This course is open to all\, with a sliding scale fee. It will be a long t
 erm series and we invite you to choose how to pay during the course. \n\n
  Please register and pay any of the choices here and we will contact you w
 ith the Zoom link for joining. 
