URL:https://anandaportland.org/events/kirtan-at-the-temple-with-ananda-gue
 sts/
SUMMARY:Kirtan at the Temple with Ananda guests
DESCRIPTION:[caption id="attachment_8548755" align="alignright" width="100"
 ] Brahmachari Sagar[/caption]\n\nKirtans are joyful events!  Come join us
  in chanting to God and opening our hearts as we spend the evening in devo
 tion. We will have Sagar and Jake from Ananda Village joining us while the
 y are here in Portland.\n\nThe first 30 minutes will be family friendly. F
 amilies with children are welcome to come and join in the fun of singing t
 o God. Children are welcome to stay after 7 PM if they are able to control
  their energy and sit still during the chants and meditation times. \n\nM
 ost chants will be in English and words will be provided. We will be toget
 her in the temple sanctuary - warm and dry.\n\nKirtans are offered free. Y
 our financial support is always appreciated.\n\n&nbsp\;\n\n\n\n&nbsp\;\n\n
 &nbsp\;\n\n&nbsp\;
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://anandaportland.org/wp-content/uploads/20
 20/06/Harmonium_Chanting.jpg
CATEGORIES:Devotional Event,Family Friendly,Kirtan/Chanting,Meditation
